# Data Dictionary

## Primary Dataset — `combined_energy.csv`

The master harmonised dataset produced by `R/cleaning/04_combine.R`. Used by RQ1, RQ2, and RQ4 dashboards.

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `country` | factor | `United Kingdom`, `United States`, or `Australia` |
| `date` | Date | First day of the month (monthly aggregation) |
| `source` | character | Standardised energy source label (see mapping below) |
| `generation_gwh` | double | Total generation for the month in gigawatt-hours (GWh) |
| `renewable` | logical | `TRUE` for Wind, Solar, Hydro, Bioenergy; `FALSE` otherwise |

**Dimensions:** 1,778 rows × 5 columns | Date range: 2019-01 to 2025-12 | 0 nulls

---

## Source Label Mapping

| Standard label | UK (GridWatch) | US (EIA code) | AU (AEMO) | Renewable? |
|----------------|----------------|---------------|-----------|:----------:|
| Gas | ccgt + ocgt | NG | Gas | No |
| Wind | wind | WND, WNB | Wind | Yes |
| Solar | solar | SUN, SNB | Solar | Yes |
| Hydro | hydro + pumped | WAT, PS | Hydro | Yes |
| Nuclear | nuclear | NUC | — | No |
| Biomass | biomass | — | — | Yes |
| Bioenergy | — | — | Bioenergy | Yes |
| Coal | — | COL | Coal | No |
| Oil | — | OIL | — | No |
| Distillate | — | — | Distillate | No |
| Geothermal | — | GEO | — | No |
| Other | — | OTH, BAT, OES, UNK, UES | — | No |

---

## Unit Conversions Applied

| Country | Raw unit | Raw granularity | Conversion formula | Output |
|---------|----------|-----------------|-------------------|--------|
| UK | MW (instantaneous) | 5-minute | MW × (5 ÷ 60) ÷ 1,000, summed monthly | GWh/month |
| US | MWh (interval total) | Daily | MWh ÷ 1,000, summed monthly | GWh/month |
| AU | GWh (monthly total) | Monthly | No conversion | GWh/month |

---

## Individual Country Files

### `uk_monthly.csv` — 504 rows × 4 columns
- Country: United Kingdom | Sources: 6 | Months: 84 (Jan 2019 – Dec 2025)
- Sources: Biomass, Gas, Hydro, Nuclear, Solar, Wind
- Note: No Coal — UK completed coal phase-out Sep 2024

### `us_monthly.csv` — 686 rows × 4 columns
- Country: United States | Sources: 9 | Months: 84 (Jan 2019 – Dec 2025)
- Sources: Coal, Gas, Geothermal, Hydro, Nuclear, Oil, Other, Solar, Wind

### `au_monthly.csv` — 2,268 rows × 4 columns
- Country: Australia | Sources: 7 | Months: 324 (Jan 1999 – Dec 2025)
- Sources: Bioenergy, Coal, Distillate, Gas, Hydro, Solar, Wind
- Note: Solar zeros before 2016, Wind zeros before 2009 (structural — pre-deployment)

---

## Australian Price & Emissions Data

Used by RQ3 only. Read directly from the raw AEMO file.
 
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `Volume Weighted Price - AUD/MWh` | double | Monthly wholesale electricity price. Value of 0 = missing (replaced with NA) |
| `Emissions Intensity - kgCO₂e/MWh` | double | Grid-average carbon intensity per MWh generated |

---

## Analytical Columns (computed in dashboards, not stored)

| Column | Computed in | Formula |
|--------|------------|---------|
| `fossil_share` | RQ1, RQ2 | sum(Coal+Gas+Oil+Distillate GWh) / total GWh × 100 |
| `ws_share` | RQ1, RQ3 | sum(Wind+Solar GWh) / total GWh × 100 |
| `renew_share` | RQ2 | sum(all renewable GWh) / total GWh × 100 |
| `hhi` | RQ4 | Σ(share_i²) × 10,000 |
| `ens` | RQ4 | 10,000 ÷ HHI |
| `reliability_gap` | RQ2 | renew_share(non-peak) − renew_share(peak) |
| `cv` | RQ3 | SD(price) / mean(price) × 100 |
